e-mail: <ccalisher@vines.colostate.edu>
[This virus, VSI, is dear to my heart. In 1965 I was involved in an
investigation of vesicular stomatitis in Abiquiui, New Mexico. Bernie
Fields, Dan Sudia, and I published the first report of the isolation of this
virus from mosquitoes, _Aedes dorsalis_ if my memory serves. -- Mod CHC]
